row.question: Bert and Ernie are among 12 tenants on Sesame Street, from which 9 tenants are to be selected for the neighborhood watch. Of the different possible selections, how many contain neither Bert nor Ernie?
row.rationale:
Removing Bert and Ernie the list will have 10 people
Question now becomes choose 9 out of 10
10! / 1!*9!
= 10
there are 10 ways to do so.
ANS: D
